  "headline": "DFM Mistakes That Add Cost to Your PCB",
  "body": [
    "Most PCB cost overruns come from avoidable design choices.",
    "Blind and buried vias can add up to 40% to fabrication costs.",
    "Dual sided assembly increases costs by 20 to 30 percent.",
    "Poor spacing causes solder bridges and rework loops.",
    "Missing or corrupted Gerber files halt production entirely."
